msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "An emulator for the Oberon RISC machine.[CR][CR]The Oberon System was designed and implemented in 1990 by professor Niklaus Wirth. It was intended for teaching computer essentials."
msgstr "Emulátor stroje Oberon RISC.[CR][CR]Systém Oberon navrhl a implementoval v roce 1990 profesor Niklaus Wirth. Byl určen pro výuku základů informatiky."
